=================================================================================
                        POWER OPTIMIZATION RECOMMENDATIONS
=================================================================================

1. Clock gating for SRAM when not accessed
   Estimated savings: 2.1 mW

2. Reduce I/O drive strength on non-critical outputs
   Estimated savings: 1.2 mW

3. Prescaler optimization for timer
   Estimated savings: 0.6 mW

4. GPIO debounce filtering optimization
   Estimated savings: 0.4 mW

5. FIFO depth optimization
   Estimated savings: 0.8 mW

Total Potential Savings: 5.1 mW (6.5% reduction)


